doctype html
html(lang="en-GB")
	head
		meta(charset="utf-8")
		title Play Cylinder Chess Online For Free | Cylinderchess.com
		meta(name="description", content="Enjoy realistic cylindrical gameplay on a unique animated 3D board; or choose traditional square geometry. Play against friends. No sign-up needed and no ads!")
		link(rel='stylesheet', href='styles/font.css')
		link(rel='stylesheet', href='styles/init-game-states.css')
		link(rel='stylesheet', href='styles/styles.css')
		link(rel='stylesheet', href='styles/mobile-styles.css')
		link(rel="apple-touch-icon", sizes="180x180", href="/assets/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png")
		link(rel="icon", type="image/png", sizes="32x32", href="/assets/favicon/favicon-32x32.png")
		link(rel="icon", type="image/png", sizes="16x16", href="/assets/favicon/favicon-16x16.png")
		link(rel="manifest", href="/assets/favicon/site.webmanifest")
		meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
	
	body(style=`--pricol: 110,145,119; --seccol: 60,60,60; --tricol: 220,220,220; --bgcol: 40,40,40;  --secbgcol: 30,30,30; --darkpricol:	66,92,72;`,class='inhome')
		a(href="https://www.cylinderchess.com")
			img#cc-graphic(alt='graphic',src='/assets/cc-logo.svg')
		#cylinder-title
			a(href="https://www.cylinderchess.com") cylinderchess.com
		include ui-components
		#helpbtn(title='Help')
			+inversemainbutton('help','?')
		#main.state-home
			#democyl
			#mainbuttonsrow
				#gamebuttonscontainer.splitbuttonrow
					+mainbutton('startbutton','Start Game')
					+mainbutton('joinbutton','Join Game')
				#sharebuttonscontainer.splitbuttonrow
					+inversemainbutton('aboutbutton','About')
					+inversemainbuttonicon('sharebutton','Share','/assets/share_light.svg')
			#startgame
				+startgameoptions()
			#joingame
				+joingameoptions()
			#waitingarea
				#waitingbg
				#waitingareacontent
					h2.titlebanner(style="text-align: center;") Waiting Room
					h3.subtitlebanner(style="text-align: center;")
						| Share with your opponent:
					h3.room(title='Copy to clipboard') 1000
					+inversesubbutton('leavewaitingroom','&larr; leave waiting room','')
			#gamearea
				#endgamerow.buttonrow
					+inversesubbutton('leaveroom','leave room','')
					+buttonrowmsg('gameovermsg','message')
					+inversesubbutton('offerdraw','offer draw','')
					+buttonrowmsg('drawoffersent','offer sent')
					+subbutton('acceptdraw','accept draw','')
					+inversesubbutton('resigngame','resign game','lastbutton')
					+inversesubbutton('offerrematch','rematch','lastbutton')
					+buttonrowmsg('rematchoffersent','rematch sent')
					+subbutton('acceptrematch','accept rematch','lastbutton')
				#boardarea
					+popup('boardpopup')
					#yourmoveslider
						| Your Move
			#sharearea
				h2.titlebanner Share
				.qrrow
					div
						p Here's a QR code --><br>and below is the URL.<br>So please share if you<br>like cylinderchess :)
					img#qr(alt='qr',src='/assets/qr.png')
				.copytext(title='Copy to Clipboard')
					p.tocopy https://www.cylinderchess.com
					img.clipboard-copy(alt='copy to clipboard',src='/assets/light-clipboard-copy.svg')
				.buttonrow
					+inversesubbutton('backsharearea','&larr; back','')
			#aboutarea
				h2.titlebanner About
				#abouttxtarea
					p 
						img(id='toby-pic', alt='Tobias Loader', src='/assets/Toby-Col-sq.jpeg')
						| Hi, I'm Tobias Loader. I'm a student at the University of Oxford studying Maths and CompSci and I love building fun coding projects.
					p Check out my 
						a(class='linkedin',href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/tobiasloader/') LinkedIn
						|  and 
						a(class='github',href='https://github.com/TobiasLoader') GitHub
						|  if you'd like more info.
					p While playing chess one day with my old school-friend Will, we said, "Let's imagine we've glued the A and H files together" â€“ effectively turning the board into a cylinder, enabling continuous movement around it. Having discovered how interesting and complex this variant can be, I thought I'd have a go at building this cylinder chess app as my holiday project. I've enjoyed playing it online with friends and hope you do too!
					p If you have any feature requests, bug reports, etc, you can get in touch via 
						a(id="email-address",href="")
						| .
					p I'm keen to keep developing this project and have plans in the pipes for user accounts, an evaluation engine and Elo rating, and matching random players. Thanks very much :)
				.buttonrow
					+inversesubbutton('backaboutarea','&larr; back','')
			+popup('generalpopup')
		#copyright-content
			p#desktop-copyright
				a.footer-link(href='https://www.cylinderchess.com') cylinderchess.com
				| &nbsp;|&nbsp;copyright&nbsp;
				span(style='font-family:Arial, sans-serif;') &copy;&nbsp;
				| &nbsp;2022&nbsp;
				a.footer-link(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/tobiasloader/') Tobias&nbsp;Loader
				| &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;all&nbsp;rights&nbsp;reserved
		script(src='/js/jquery.min.js')
		script(src='/socket.io/socket.io.js')
		script(type='module', src='/js/main.mjs')
		script(src='/js/ui-components.js')